flowchart TD
  start([Start]) --> triage[Triage Case]
  triage --> research[Research Public Evidence]
  research -->|Needs deeper public discovery| deep[Firecrawl Deep Discovery]
  research -->|Enough evidence to plan| plan[Plan Next Action]
  deep --> plan
  plan -->|Portal or support form| browser[Browser Runtime Path]
  plan -->|Email is strongest| email[Email Path]
  plan -->|Cannot run directly| manual[Manual Fallback]
  browser --> consent[Request Consent]
  email --> consent
  consent --> execute[Execute Case Action]
  execute --> followup[Follow-up & Resolve]
  manual --> followup
  followup --> end([End])
